# Stary Zagan, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Stary Zagan () is a rural locality (a selo) in Mukhorshibirsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 312 as of 2010. There are 9 streets.
Geography
Stary Zagan is located 5&nbsp;km southwest of Mukhorshibir (the district's administrative centre) by road. Novy Zagan is the nearest rural locality.
